data.description: Here is your opportunity to purchase a spacious home in prime location at a super reasonable price! 17 Oak Grove Lane is a 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home sitting on nearly 1 acre with plenty of space to enjoy! The home features an open floor plan concept on the main level where all 3 bedrooms are located, and you can retreat downstairs to enjoy the large bonus room that could serve as an office, play room, exercise room, entertainment room, and more! Step outside to grill on the deck and take advantage of the large fenced in level back yard perfect for pets and fun with the family! You can't beat the location of this Adairsville home conveniently positioned off of highway 140 with quick access to I-75, Calhoun, and Rome! Take the first step towards making this home yours, and schedule your showing today!
